// Datasheet for the `store` device: it requires the driver to provide storage for its `Node` shape,
// at least 4 rows. `Node` is the shared GLOBAL shape (`.ds.arche` decls register unprefixed);
// `Node[4]` in a datasheet is a storage REQUIREMENT (minimum), never an allocation. The driver owns
// the real pool and may size it larger. Support file.
// RUN: true
Node :: arche { key :: float, val :: float }
Node[4]
